</article>
</div>
<p>Awesome, right? Well, we don‚Äôt stop there! With the details they provided in their on-boarding survey, we‚Äôll send targeted emails during their training process that aligns perfectly with their goals and experience level.</p>
<p>For example, let‚Äôs say that Erin just got started with paid search advertising, so she‚Äôs at a beginner level status. Her main goal is to <a href="/conversion-rate-optimization">increase conversions</a> in her company‚Äôs AdWords account. She‚Äôll receive educational content that is geared toward beginners and focused on increasing conversions (since that‚Äôs her ultimate goal). Here are some examples‚Ä¶</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="8d3d28a7-5097-46bb-a496-dc243779d55f" data-langcode="en">
