</div>
<p>To take it another step further, since Erin told us she works in the Travel industry, we‚Äôll send her PPC content relevant to her work.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="173864a4-fd97-4d96-bde7-09f3c4cd5bc3" data-langcode="en">
